Components

Things to recognize in each Components

[Mesh]
- Mesh

[Mesh Renderer]
- Materials
- Cast Shadows

[Skinned Mesh Renderer]
- Root Bones

[Particle System]
- Emission
- Shape
(there are lots)

[Rigidbody]
- Drag
- Mass
- Gravity

[Box Collider]
- Edit Collider

[Sphere Collider]
- Radius

[Capsule Collider]
- Radius 
- Height


[Rigidbody 2D]
- Auto Mass

[Box Collider]
- x , y

[Circle Collider]
- x, y
- radius

[Audio Listener]
- picking up audio from a location (hearing audio)

[Audio Source]
- Audio clip
- output
- mute
- 3d sound setting

[Audio Reverb Zone]
- Reverb preset (cave, hanger etc)

[Rendering Camera]
- Culling Mask
- Field of View
- Projection
- Target Texture
- Depth
- View port

[Rendering Light]
- Range
- Intensity
- Flare
- Halo

[Rendering Canvas Renderer]
*ex UI Text, UI Button, UI Image
- Child of canvas


[Canvas GameObject]
- Canvas
- Canvas Scaler

[User Defined Script]
- Adding a Script Component
(New Behaviour Script) 

- Attaching this instead of using the Unity's built in script(s) to manipulate

